ngs.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-Clyro-limited-edition-vinyl-pressings.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-Clyro-limited-edition-vinyl-pressings.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-Clyro-limited-edition-vinyl-pressings.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-Clyro-limited-edition-vinyl-pressings.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-Clyro-limited-edition-vinyl-pressings.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Biffy-Clyro">Biffy Clyro</a>在他们的“A Celebration of Beginnings”巡演之前宣布了他们前三张专辑的限量版。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/biffy-clyro-myth-happily-ever-after-interview-dan-martin-scott-hutchison-2021-3078721">比菲·克莱罗 (Biffy Clyro) 接受采访时表示：“我们正在制作我们版本的《美国白痴》——它的名字叫《苏格兰旋钮！》</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队在伦敦和格拉斯哥举行的六场门票全部售完的演出是为了庆祝他们的专辑《Blackened Sky》（2002 年）、《The Vertigo of Bliss》（2003 年）和《Infinity Land》（2004 年）。由西蒙·尼尔（Simon Neil）和双胞胎本·约翰斯顿（Ben Johnston）和詹姆斯·约翰斯顿（James Johnston）组成的苏格兰摇滚乐队将在演出中纪念他们的早年生活，并在每晚完整地演奏一张专辑以及其他密纹唱片中的精选曲目。</p><p>三张专辑的限量版黑胶唱片只能从乐队的演出现场、他们的<a href="https://store.biffyclyro.com/gb/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方网站</a>和 Beggars Arkive<a href="https://archive.beggars.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网上商店</a>购买。 《Blackened Sky》将以橙色、黑色和透明的泼墨形式压制，而《The Vertigo of Bliss》将以白色和黄色的墨点压制，而《Infinity Land》将以蓝色和白色的螺旋桨压制。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804118" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804118" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804118" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Biffy-clyro-blackened-sky-1x1-LP.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Biffy clyro &#39;Blackened Sky&#39; 1x1 LP。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" heig